&ug 0x00FF80  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug 0x00FF80  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
