&ug BLACK  &ug 0xFF00FF  &ug 0x00FFFF  &ug GREEN  &ug YELLOW  &ug 0x6B1FCE                                   &ug BLACK  &ug YELLOW  &ug GREEN  &ug 0x00FFFF  &ug 0xFF00FF  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug 0x6B1FCE  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
