        Cursor {
            bindings = <
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                                     &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug 0x00FF80  &ug BLACK  &ug 0x00FF80  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug GREEN  &ug 0x99F5FF  &ug RED  &ug 0x99F5FF  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug YELLOW  &ug 0xFF00FF  &ug 0x00FFFF  &ug GREEN  &ug YELLOW  &ug BLACK                                   &ug GREEN  &ug RED  &ug RED  &ug RED  &ug BLACK  &ug YELLOW
&ug 0x00FF80  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0x7A00FF  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug GREEN  &ug 0x00FF80  &ug 0x99F5FF  &ug 0x99F5FF  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
