        Number {
            bindings = <
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                                     &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug GREEN  &ug BLACK
