&ug YELLOW  &ug 0xFF00FF  &ug 0x00FFFF  &ug GREEN  &ug YELLOW  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0xFF7C4D  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug BLUE  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug 0xFF80BF  &ug BLACK  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug 0xFFD900  &ug RED  &ug BLACK
