&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK                                   &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
&ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug RED  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK  &ug BLACK
