&kp LG(L)  &kp LG(A)  &select_line   &select_word   &kp LG(F)  &none  &none   &none  &none  &select_none  &extend_line  &extend_word  &kp LG(V)  &kp LG(L)     &kp PG_UP      &kp PG_DN      &none          &none
